BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury trine Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Cancer 7°26’) - trine - Natal Jupiter \nThis transit is favourable for trips, any type of learning and education, writing, and relationships with the public and lawyers. Your mind is overflowing with optimism, and it is easy for other people to work with you. You may be promoted at work or you may receive an interesting offer.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 9th house: \nNow is one of the best times for studying and career development. If you want to enrol in a university or start looking for a new job, do it now!  \nNow you are a great storyteller and other people will love listening to your stories. You can fully use your creativity when writing, learning and communicating with people, especially those from university environment and from other cultures. Now you can also learn new languages with ease. Overall, you will be tolerant of alternative views, ideas and thoughts. It is also possible that you will get a great new idea that will bring you success.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:19740604T230400Z
DTEND:19740604T230400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165103Z
UID:8_tr_me_tr_ju
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Saturn square Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Saturn (Cancer 5°03’) - square - Natal Pluto \nYou may be surrounded by people who have bad intentions. If you have suppressed the problems you have with others, they will now resurface. Power struggles and manipulations may occur. You should therefore try to protect yourself from all the negative energy that may come your way, but avoid being negative towards others, as this may leave you vulnerable.  \n \nTransit Saturn in Natal 9th house: \nWith this transit, Saturn forces you to review your principles, beliefs and ideals. This will be associated with questions such as: “Where am I heading and what am I trying to achieve for a better future?”, “What principles do I stand for and what do I believe in?”. The previous system of belief and ideals may suddenly seem shallow to you. You will also work on improving your self-confidence. If you are studying, you may wonder if you have chosen the right field. In general, you will be more focused on your personal development. At the end of this transit, you will have a much more stable system of beliefs and you will be more self-confident. You will be aware of what you want and where you are heading. You may have to deal with problems when you are traveling abroad, or you may get legal/judicial problems. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:19740604T232400Z
DTEND:19740604T232400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165103Z
UID:9_tr_sa_sq_pl
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus sextile Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Taurus 7°26’) - sextile - Natal Jupiter \nThis transit will make you feel happy and satisfied. You will enjoy even the slightest pleasure and pass this feeling on to others. Nothing will upset you. You may also feel a bit lazy and seek pleasure. Your relationships will flourish. In the area of finance, you may make a good investment, or you may get a great opportunity to acquire finances. If you are dealing with legal issues, this transit will contribute to a satisfactory outcome. It is a great time for social events, excursions or a vacation.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 7th house: \nYou and your partner will be very much in love. You will prefer to spend time only the two of you rather than go out with friends. If you are single, you will be keen to start a new, functioning relationship and find a new partner. In relationships with other people you will use flattery to get what you want. However, be honest! If you are fighting with your partner or a close friend, you will probably reconcile your problems and make up. It is an ideal time for marriage and business partnerships.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
