DTSTART:19740617T124900Z
DTEND:19740617T124900Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165103Z
UID:26_tr_ve_tr_pl
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun trine Uranus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Gemini 25°58’) - trine - Natal Uranus \nYou feel restless, you want to express your individuality and stand out in the crowd. Your plans will be fulfilled faster than you expect, and new opportunities may arise. You will be full of new ideas and new perspectives.  \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 9th house: \nIt’s time to expand your horizons! This transit usually brings new discoveries.  \nYou may have the urge to seek the meaning of life and you will be open to alternative views. It is a good time to travel longer distances and get to know different cultures. If you are not traveling anywhere, you can expect more interactions with people from other countries or different backgrounds. There may be problems with your father.  \nIt is also an ideal time for education, especially in the field of philosophy, where you will be more interested in various religious movements. If you already belong to a religion, more intensive engagement is expected - for example, you can go to church more often, engage in church activities, etc. During this period, you will also listen more to your guts and intuition. At the same time, you will not be afraid to discuss these topics with others because this transit supports sincerity. But be careful not to be rude and intolerant.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:19740617T132600Z
DTEND:19740617T132600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165103Z
UID:27_tr_su_tr_ur
END:VEVENT
