SUMMARY:Tr. Sun conjunction Saturn
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Gemini 29°22’) - conjunction - Natal Saturn \nYour sense of duty, honour and tradition will increase. Work and family affairs may become too tiring. It is an ideal time for commitment to long-term projects. You may feel isolated and misunderstood while you are pursuing your ambitions. \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 9th house: \nIt’s time to expand your horizons! This transit usually brings new discoveries.  \nYou may have the urge to seek the meaning of life and you will be open to alternative views. It is a good time to travel longer distances and get to know different cultures. If you are not traveling anywhere, you can expect more interactions with people from other countries or different backgrounds. There may be problems with your father.  \nIt is also an ideal time for education, especially in the field of philosophy, where you will be more interested in various religious movements. If you already belong to a religion, more intensive engagement is expected - for example, you can go to church more often, engage in church activities, etc. During this period, you will also listen more to your guts and intuition. At the same time, you will not be afraid to discuss these topics with others because this transit supports sincerity. But be careful not to be rude and intolerant.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
