BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Saturn trine Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Saturn (Cancer 7°26’) - trine - Natal Jupiter \nThis transit will make you extremely productive and you will have a lot of enthusiasm to work. You will be practical and confident in your own abilities. If you have any unfinished work, now it is the perfect time to get to it and finish it. It is a good time to use your productivity to achieve great results and increase your authority. \n \nTransit Saturn in Natal 9th house: \nWith this transit, Saturn forces you to review your principles, beliefs and ideals. This will be associated with questions such as: “Where am I heading and what am I trying to achieve for a better future?”, “What principles do I stand for and what do I believe in?”. The previous system of belief and ideals may suddenly seem shallow to you. You will also work on improving your self-confidence. If you are studying, you may wonder if you have chosen the right field. In general, you will be more focused on your personal development. At the end of this transit, you will have a much more stable system of beliefs and you will be more self-confident. You will be aware of what you want and where you are heading. You may have to deal with problems when you are traveling abroad, or you may get legal/judicial problems. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:19740623T170700Z
DTEND:19740623T170700Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165103Z
UID:34_tr_sa_tr_ju
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars trine Neptune
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Leo 9°22’) - trine - Natal Neptune \nYou will tend to put the needs of others before your own. It is a good time to devote some of your time to charity and volunteering. You will not feel very motivated to move ahead and take on a leading role. Be careful not to miss a deadline and beware of procrastination.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 10th house: \nDuring this transit you will start putting more energy into your work. You will start thinking about your ambitions and try to find ways to achieve your goals. You may start thinking about changing your profession; you may even want to start your own business. In any case, you are going to actively approach all the challenges ahead. Beware, this transit can cause pedantic behaviour, criticism and egoism, which lead to conflicts and unnecessary arguments.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
