BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus sextile Mercury
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Taurus 28°55’) - sextile - Natal Mercury \nYou will be able to explain your ideas to other people with ease. If you are worried about something, you will go straight to the point and it will be easy to explain the cause of the problem. You will also be a great mediator. Any negotiation under your leadership will be favourable, including if you want to make up with somebody you have had a fight with. You will be more creative than usual, so you should let your ideas and thoughts flow freely. If you feel nervous, try to relax in a way that is pleasant for you.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 8th house: \nDuring this transit you will feel the desire for a deep intimate bond with your loved ones. You will be attracted to the people with something mysterious about them; perhaps you will feel a bit stirred by them. Shallow people will not deserve your attention now. Sexual relationships will deepen and make you feel much younger and full of energy. You may feel an increase in sexual energy. You may also see a psychologist or meet someone who is one during this transit. \nIn your romantic relationship you will deal with various issues, including intimacy, finance, and power distribution. It is possible that either you or your partner will want to move your commitment to the next level.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
